description:
How can you be sure you are a true Christian?

There are billions of Christians worldwide, yet there is widespread concern over what it means to be a Christian.

This #short clip from the Global Campmeeting sermon, How Do We Know Our Way To Salvation? by Jill Morikone
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=okQScCqQMdc&list=PL-k2Gb-DBYo9tb9fHW_AxGxJ1R8MpNnpa&index=9  discusses, from the Scriptures, how a good Christian lives his life. Being a Christian entails resembling and reflecting God's characteristics, being gracious and compassionate to others, and loving them as the Father loves each of us.

Watch the full video to learn more about how we can achieve salvation by becoming true disciples of Christ.
